name: The Split Traveler - Full Release
description:
This is a Academic game project made in collaboration by 3 Arts and Entertainment Technologies students at The University of Texas at Austin. 

This game is a 2D puzzle platformer built around swapping between 2 slightly different dimensions! 

Credits:

- Original Music & SFX by John Chambers

- Original Assets made by  The Team 

- Extra Tree, Rock, and House Assets provided by "reach the enD"
